Package com.im.njams.sdk.configuration

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConfigurationProvider
    This interface must be implemented for creating new ConfigurationProvider
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActivityConfiguration
    Settings container for activities.
    Configuration
    The configuration contains all configuration of the client, which are not part of the initial settings, and therefore could be changed by the client instance, or via instructions.
    ConfigurationInstructionListener
    InstructionListener implementation for all instructions which will modify configuration values.
    ConfigurationProviderFactory
    Creates the ConfigurationProvider, which has been specified in the settings properties;
    ProcessConfiguration
    Settings container for processes.
    ProcessFilter
    This class implements filtering processes based on the runtime Configuration.
    ProcessFilterEntry
    Defines a filter to be matched against process paths.
    TracepointExt
    Extended version of the Tracepoint for storing the current iterations of a tracepoint
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ProcessFilterEntry.FilterType
    Defines the type of the filter (include or exclude)
    ProcessFilterEntry.MatcherType
    The matcher to be used when comparing the process path against the filter.
